{"id":2054,"date":"2018-03-08T13:32:16","date_gmt":"2018-03-08T08:02:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/?p=2054"},"modified":"2023-01-24T14:54:44","modified_gmt":"2023-01-24T09:24:44","slug":"hasin-jahan","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/hasin-jahan\/","title":{"rendered":"Hasin Jahan Wiki, Age, Husband, Family, Biography &amp; More"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2065\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan.jpg\" alt=\"Hasin Jahan\" width=\"450\" height=\"409\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan.jpg 450w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-300x273.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Hasin Jahan is the wife of Indian cricketer\u00a0<strong>Mohammed Shami<\/strong>. She hit the headlines in early March 2018 when she made\u00a0shocking revelations about her husband Mohammed Shami&#8217;s extra-marital affair in front of media. Check out\u00a0Hasin Jahan\u00a0Wiki, Height, Weight, Age, Boyfriend, Family, Husband, Biography, Facts &amp; More.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2066\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-1.jpg\" alt=\"Hasin Jahan\" width=\"288\" height=\"542\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-1.jpg 288w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-1-159x300.jpg 159w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 288px) 100vw, 288px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_62 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Contents<\/p>\n<label for=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce20664a47\" class=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-label\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\"  id=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce20664a47\"  aria-label=\"Toggle\" \/><nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/hasin-jahan\/#BiographyWiki\" title=\"Biography\/Wiki\">Biography\/Wiki<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/hasin-jahan\/#Physical_Appearance\" title=\"Physical Appearance\">Physical Appearance<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/hasin-jahan\/#Family_Husband\" title=\"Family &amp; Husband\">Family &amp; Husband<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/hasin-jahan\/#Career\" title=\"Career\">Career<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/hasin-jahan\/#Controversies\" title=\"Controversies\">Controversies<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/hasin-jahan\/#Facts\" title=\"Facts\">Facts<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"BiographyWiki\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Biography\/Wiki<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Hasin was born on <strong>2 February 1980<\/strong>\u00a0in <strong>Siuri, Birbhum, West Bengal, India<\/strong>. Before marriage,\u00a0she used to work as a <strong>model<\/strong>. She always wanted to become a successful model. She even wanted to work in the entertainment industry, but due to family commitments, she left modelling.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Physical Appearance<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>She is approximately\u00a0\u00a0<strong>5\u2019 7\u201d<\/strong> tall and weighs around\u00a0<strong>55 kg<\/strong>. She has <strong>dark brown eyes<\/strong> and<strong> black hair<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-2.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-2067\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-2.jpg\" alt=\"Hasin Jahan\" width=\"343\" height=\"581\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-2.jpg 400w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-2-177x300.jpg 177w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 343px) 100vw, 343px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family_Husband\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Family &amp; Husband<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>She belongs to a <strong>Muslim Bengali<\/strong> family. Her father <strong>Mohammed Hassan<\/strong> is a Kolkata-based businessman and runs a transportation business. Her mother is a homemaker.<\/p>\n<p>She first married,\u00a0<strong>Sheikh Saifuddin<\/strong> of her native locality in 2002, and were blessed with <strong>2 daughters<\/strong>. After having kids, she wanted to continue with her studies, but her husband&#8217;s family was against it, which later became the core reason for their divorce in 2010.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-first-husband-Sheikh-Saifuddin.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-2134\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-first-husband-Sheikh-Saifuddin.jpg\" alt=\"Hasin Jahan first husband Sheikh Saifuddin\" width=\"381\" height=\"428\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-first-husband-Sheikh-Saifuddin.jpg 485w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-first-husband-Sheikh-Saifuddin-267x300.jpg 267w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 381px) 100vw, 381px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>On\u00a0<strong>6 June 2014<\/strong>, she got married for the second time to her boyfriend cum Indian cricketer\u00a0<strong>Mohammed Shami<\/strong>. The couple has a daughter\u00a0<strong>Aairah Shami<\/strong> who was born in <strong>July 2015<\/strong>. In 2018, the couple got separated.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-with-her-husband-Mohammed-Shami-and-daughter-Aairah-Shami.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2068\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-with-her-husband-Mohammed-Shami-and-daughter-Aairah-Shami.jpg\" alt=\"Hasin Jahan with her husband Mohammed Shami and daughter Aairah Shami\" width=\"400\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-with-her-husband-Mohammed-Shami-and-daughter-Aairah-Shami.jpg 400w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-with-her-husband-Mohammed-Shami-and-daughter-Aairah-Shami-240x300.jpg 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Career<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>She did her schooling at\u00a0<strong>Katwa Bharati Bhaban, Katwa<\/strong> and completed her <strong>graduation<\/strong> from the <strong>University of Calcutta, Kolkata<\/strong>. She started her career as a model at a very young age and did numerous modelling assignments. However, she left the modelling after marriage.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-3.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2069\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-3.jpg\" alt=\"Hasin Jahan\" width=\"332\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-3.jpg 332w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-3-199x300.jpg 199w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 332px) 100vw, 332px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Controversies\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Controversies<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>In December 2016, her\u00a0husband Shami posted a pic of himself with her, which was criticized by fanatic Muslims as she was wearing a sleeveless dress.\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-sleeveless-dress.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-2136\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-sleeveless-dress.jpg\" alt=\"Hasin Jahan sleeveless dress\" width=\"393\" height=\"391\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-sleeveless-dress.jpg 479w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-sleeveless-dress-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-sleeveless-dress-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 393px) 100vw, 393px\" \/><\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In March 2018, she alleged that her husband and his family tortured her for more than two years and also tried to kill her several times. She\u00a0even previously informed the <strong>Jadavpur Police Station<\/strong> in January 2018\u00a0about him and his family verbally but at that time, she didn&#8217;t take any legal action.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>She also alleged that her husband has extra-marital affair. She posted his chat screenshots with other women on different social media platforms. According to her, her husband has also married a girl from Pakistan.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>On 23 January 2023, Mohammed Shami was ordered to pay her alimony of Rs. 1.30 lakh per month by a Kolkata court. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_2054_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_2054_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_2054_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_2054_1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_2054_1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/zeenews.india.com\/cricket\/big-blow-to-mohammed-shami-as-cricketer-ordered-to-pay-rs-1-3-lakh-monthly-as-alimony-to-estranged-wife-hasin-jahan-2565044.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Zee News<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Facts\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Facts<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>She first met\u00a0<strong>Mohammed Shami<\/strong> in 2012 during an IPL season.\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-with-Mohammed-Shami.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2070\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-with-Mohammed-Shami.jpg\" alt=\"Hasin Jahan with Mohammed Shami\" width=\"320\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-with-Mohammed-Shami.jpg 320w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/Hasin-Jahan-with-Mohammed-Shami-240x300.jpg 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" \/><\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>She loves <strong>travelling<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>There was a rumour\u00a0that she is a close friend of <strong>Sakshi Dhoni<\/strong>, wife of <strong>MS Dhoni<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>She is a huge fan of Bangladesh\u00a0Prime Minister\u00a0<strong>Sheikh Hasina Wazed<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div><div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_label_expand_2054_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_2054_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_2054_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_2054_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">References<\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_button_plus_2054_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button\" on=